<view class="container">
  <view class="header">
    <view class="header-icon">
      <text class="header-icon-text">📤</text>
    </view>
    <view class="header-title">文件上传</view>
    <view class="header-desc">上传文件生成分享链接</view>
  </view>

  <view class="card">
    <view class="card-title">选择文件</view>
    
    <view class="upload-area" bindtap="chooseFile">
      <view class="upload-icon">
        <text class="upload-icon-text">📁</text>
      </view>
      <view class="upload-text">点击选择文件</view>
      <view class="upload-hint">支持从手机文件系统或聊天记录选择</view>
      <view class="upload-formats">支持格式：PPT、PPTX、PDF、Word、Excel、图片、压缩包等</view>
    </view>

    <view wx:if="fileName" class="file-info">
      <view class="file-icon">
        <text class="file-icon-text">{{ getFileExtension(fileName) }}</text>
      </view>
      <view class="file-detail">
        <view class="file-name">{{ fileName }}</view>
        <view class="file-size">文件大小：{{ formatFileSize(fileSize) }}</view>
      </view>
      <view class="file-actions">
        <view class="action-btn" bindtap="resetUpload">重新选择</view>
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view wx:if="lastError" class="card error-card">
    <view class="error-header">
      <text class="error-icon">⚠️</text>
      <text class="error-title">上传失败</text>
    </view>
    <view class="error-content">{{ lastError }}</view>
    <view class="error-actions">
      <button class="btn-error-retry" bindtap="chooseFile">重新选择文件</button>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view wx:if="fileName && !lastError" class="card">
    <view class="card-title">分享设置</view>
    
    <view class="config-item">
      <view class="config-label">最大下载次数</view>
      <view class="config-input-wrap">
        <input 
          class="config-input" 
          type="digit" 
          value="{{ remainingDownloads }}" 
          bindinput="onRemainingDownloadsChange"
          placeholder="10"
        />
        <text class="config-unit">次</text>
      </view>
    </view>
    
    <view class="config-item">
      <view class="config-label">有效期限</view>
      <view class="config-input-wrap">
        <input 
          class="config-input" 
          type="digit" 
          value="{{ expireDays }}" 
          bindinput="onExpireDaysChange"
          placeholder="7"
        />
        <text class="config-unit">天</text>
      </view>
    </view>
    
    <view class="config-hint">
      <text>下载次数：1-1000 次</text>
      <text>有效期：1-365 天</text>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view wx:if="showShareLink" class="card">
    <view class="card-title">✓ 上传成功</view>
    
    <view class="success-box">
      <view class="success-icon">
        <text class="success-icon-text">🎉</text>
      </view>
      <view class="success-text">文件已成功上传并生成分享链接</view>
    </view>

    <view class="share-section">
      <view class="share-label">分享链接</view>
      <view class="share-link">{{ shareUrl }}</view>
      <button class="btn-copy" bindtap="copyLink">复制链接</button>
    </view>

    <view class="share-info">
      <view class="info-item">
        <text class="info-icon">📊</text>
        <text class="info-text">剩余下载次数：{{ remainingDownloads }} 次</text>
      </view>
      <view class="info-item">
        <text class="info-icon">⏰</text>
        <text class="info-text">有效期限：{{ expireDays }} 天</text>
      </view>
    </view>

    <button class="btn-another" bindtap="resetUpload">继续上传</button>
  </view>

  <view wx:if="fileName && !showShareLink && !lastError" class="card">
    <view class="btn-area">
      <button 
        class="btn-primary {{ !fileName || isUploading ? 'btn-disabled' : '' }}" 
        bindtap="uploadFile"
        disabled="{{ !fileName || isUploading }}"
      >
        {{ isUploading ? '上传中...' : '上传并生成链接' }}
      </button>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="tip">
    <view class="tip-text">
      将生成的链接粘贴到公众号文章中，粉丝即可点击下载学习资料。
    </view>
    <view class="tip-text-small">
      提示：PPT、Word、Excel等文件在微信内置浏览器中可能无法直接预览，建议另存为PDF格式后上传兼容性更好
    </view>
  </view>
</view>